# Mirpanel Public Discovery Resources

Mirpanel exposes a small set of public discovery resources for crawlers and agents.

## Resources

- Homepage: https://mirpanel.com/
- Sitemap: https://mirpanel.com/sitemap.xml
- Robots: https://mirpanel.com/robots.txt
- API Catalog: https://mirpanel.com/.well-known/api-catalog
- Agent Card: https://mirpanel.com/.well-known/agent-card.json
- Status: https://mirpanel.com/.well-known/status
- OpenAPI description: https://mirpanel.com/.well-known/openapi.json

## Public API Scope

This catalog only describes public discovery resources. Mirpanel admin pages, login routes, tokens, private APIs, GitHub integration endpoints and other internal management endpoints are not part of the public API catalog.
